<!--
Template: image-inset-card
Description: Serper image as an inset media panel with adjacent news/explainer text.

Runtime rendering is implemented by:
src/renderer/hyperframesTemplateSystem.js

Image flow:
1. Scene-planning prompt returns keyword-image for this template.
2. Pipeline calls Serper, downloads usable images, and stores local session paths.
3. TemplateData prompt receives this sample plus downloadedImages.
4. OpenAI chooses one local image path and fills templateData.image.src.
-->
<section class="scene-template-image-inset-card" data-template="image-inset-card">
  <pre data-template-data>{{templateData}}</pre>
</section>
